## `DisposableStore` â€” The Collection (`lifecycle.ts:416`)

`DisposableStore` is the workhorse. It manages a `Set<IDisposable>` and handles several edge cases:

| Method | Behavior |
|---|---|
| `add(o)` | Adds to the set; warns (not throws) if already disposed â€” the item leaks |
